I don't know if it can be relevant or not but it looks like multimedia/ffmpeg is either culprit or at least involved. Below are the lines 80-84 of the file h264_decoder_impl.cc

// Called by FFmpeg when it is done with a frame buffer, see AVGetBuffer2.
void AVFreeBuffer2(void* opaque, uint8_t* data) {
  VideoFrame* video_frame = static_cast<VideoFrame*>(opaque);
  delete video_frame;
}
